'''Zorp House''' was an apartment building on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. In [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]], [[Dark Lord of the Sith/Legends|Dark Lady of the Sith]] [[Lumiya]] had an [[Apartment three hundred seven twelve|apartment]] on the three hundredth floor. It was later found by [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke]] and [[Mara Jade Skywalker]] after Lumiya participated in the death of [[Tresina Lobi]]. It had a [[Neimoidian/Legends|Neimoidian]] [[Zorp House building manager|building manager]] and contained 25,000 apartments. The universal passcode for the tower was [[red seven, blue twelve, green zero zero]].<ref name="Tempest">''[[Legacy of the Force: Tempest]]''</ref>

